                              <span className="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-lg bg-green-100 text-luGreen-dark text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Event</span>
                              <h4 className="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-luGreen-dark transition-colors">Grand Alumni Homecoming 2025</h4>
                              <p className="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Join us for a night of memories, networking, and celebration at the newly renovated Laguna Sports Complex. Early bird registration is now open.</p>
                          </div>
                          <div className="text-right flex flex-col items-end">
                              <span className="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400">2 days ago</span>
                              <div className="mt-4 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transform translate-x-4 group-hover:translate-x-0 transition-all duration-300">
